person_info()

summary: The person info results for this page of data. remarks: The person id of the last PersonInfo element in this list should be used as the person id cursor parameter for the next call to this method. If this list is empty and the request included a person id cursor, then there are no more authorized people to page through. If the list is empty and the request did not include a person id cursor, there are no people authorized for the application. returns: a HealthVault::WCData::Types::PersonInfo Array
